# Performance & Load Testing Strategy

## Objectives
- Validate system stability under load
- Identify performance bottlenecks
- Ensure acceptable response time

## Scope
- Critical user flows
- API endpoints
- Major business transactions

## Key Metrics
- Response time
- Throughput
- Error rate
- System resource usage

## Execution Approach
- Baseline testing
- Load testing
- Stress testing
- Spike testing

## Tools
JMeter / k6 / Gatling (future automation)

## Success Criteria
- Stable application behavior
- Acceptable response time
- No critical failures
